Title: Stick It
Plot:
Alan once again goes to bat for Melissa, this time with much less confidence, who is in serious trouble with the IRS.

Meanwhile, Paul and Brad enact a plan to help Rachel get into rehab, and Denise re-enters the world of dating with disastrous results.
GuestStars: Ashley Rios,  Josh Braaten,  Bradley James,  Robert Joseph,  Shelley Berman,  Jayne Brook,  Scott Paulin,  April Rios,  Laura Henry,  Zylan Brooks,  Matthew Lenhart,  Kevin Isola,  Michael Hilow,  Brad Bovee
